snippet: The defending champion, Ronnie O’Sullivan, breezed into the world championship semifinals with a session to spare after completing a 13-3 win over Shaun Murphy.
abstract: Ronnie O'Sullivan defeats Shaun Murphy, 13-3, to advance into the snooker world championship semifinals.
lead_paragraph: The defending champion, Ronnie O’Sullivan, breezed into the world championship semifinals with a session to spare after completing a 13-3 win over Shaun Murphy.
